<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 03:22:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：澳大利亚附近的中国直播警告感到惊讶的航空公司飞行员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/airline-pilots-surprised-by-chinese-live-fire-warning-near-australia-messages-2025-02-28/</link><description>飞行员上周已经在澳大利亚附近的中国直播海军演习中首次听说，收到的消息迫使一些人通过繁忙的空中走廊，卫星短信，路透社看到的飞行员的卫星短信，卫星短信。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 03:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/airline-pilots-surprised-by-chinese-live-fire-warning-near-australia-messages-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>新世界发展的债务偿还重点，预计H1损失为8.75亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/new-world-developments-debt-repayment-focus-amid-875-million-expected-h1-loss-2025-02-28/</link><description>在过去三年中，香港的新世界发展一直在与流动性压力作斗争，该公司将在周五报告临时净亏损高达8.75亿美元，受到长时间的财产低迷和高利息成本的伤害。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 02:41:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/new-world-developments-debt-repayment-focus-amid-875-million-expected-h1-loss-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促思考大事，努力恢复受虐的消费</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urged-think-big-go-hard-reviving-battered-consumption-2025-02-28/</link><description>可可温利利用中国的消费者补贴以大约三分之二的原始价格购买了新iPhone。同时，她正在削减其他事情。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:05:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urged-think-big-go-hard-reviving-battered-consumption-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>大使说，中国不会为澳大利亚东部的军事演习道歉。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-will-not-apologise-military-drills-off-australias-east-ambassador-says-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国驻澳大利亚大使说，周五，他的国家没有理由为在澳大利亚和新西兰之间的国际水域进行的军事演习道歉，这些军事演习迫使至少49次飞行以改变路径。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 23:47:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-will-not-apologise-military-drills-off-australias-east-ambassador-says-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国科技创业公司竞赛，利用XI会议的DeepSeek Fever</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-tech-startups-race-capitalise-deepseek-fever-xis-meeting-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国技术初创公司正在竞争新鲜的筹款活动，以利用深发现的对人工智能的热情，以及习近平总统最近对该国私人企业的支持。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 23:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-tech-startups-race-capitalise-deepseek-fever-xis-meeting-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>官员说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mexico-analyzing-more-measures-crack-down-low-cost-shipments-official-says-2025-02-27/</link><description>一位官员周四表示，墨西哥正在权衡进一步的贸易措施，以打击低成本的货物，这是一位大部分来自中国的所谓“ de Minimis”购买后的关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:32:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mexico-analyzing-more-measures-crack-down-low-cost-shipments-official-says-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国制造商Hikvision未能推翻我们对设备批准的禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-rejects-hikvision-bid-lift-fcc-ban-equipment-approvals-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国上诉法院周四拒绝了Hikvision的竞标，要求取消联邦通信委员会对中国制造商生产的新视频监视和电信设备的批准。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:13:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-rejects-hikvision-bid-lift-fcc-ban-equipment-approvals-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国谴责泰国的40个Uyghurs返回中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-condemns-thailands-return-40-uyghurs-china-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国国务卿马可·卢比奥（Marco Rubio）周四谴责泰国至少40名乌耶（Uyghurs）返回中国，华盛顿说，穆斯林集团的成员面临种族灭绝。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:05:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-condemns-thailands-return-40-uyghurs-china-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国销售调查的前商务官员说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/big-fines-coming-companies-with-export-violations-says-ex-commerce-official-2025-02-27/</link><description>上个月最高部门官员说，在未来几个月内，美国商务部可能会在未来几个月内向像中国这样的国家提供非法运送技术的公司处以高额罚款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 17:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/big-fines-coming-companies-with-export-violations-says-ex-commerce-official-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国商务提名人说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/report-tsmc-chips-made-huawei-huge-concern-us-commerce-nominee-says-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的提名人周四负责监督出口政策，称台湾半导体制造业公司共同生产了成千上万的筹码，这些筹码进入了中国的华为，这是“巨大的关注”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 16:53:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/report-tsmc-chips-made-huawei-huge-concern-us-commerce-nominee-says-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>苹果提起手表的“碳中性”主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-sued-over-carbon-neutral-claim-watches-2025-02-27/</link><description>苹果曾被消费者起诉，他们说其说明三种版本的苹果手表是“碳中性”的，环保友好的是虚假和误导性的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:30:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-sued-over-carbon-neutral-claim-watches-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>COP30总裁说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-plays-key-role-climate-change-may-be-looked-additional-leadership-cop30-2025-02-27/</link><description>COP30主席安德烈·阿兰哈·科雷亚·洛戈（Andre Aranha Correa do Lago Lago）周四表示，中国在应对气候变化方面起着非常重要的作用，其他人可能会寻求亚洲国家的额外领导地位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:23:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-plays-key-role-climate-change-may-be-looked-additional-leadership-cop30-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普誓言3月4日对加拿大墨西哥的关税，中国超过芬太尼的10％</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-says-mexico-canada-tariffs-take-effect-march-4-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周四表示，他提议对墨西哥的25％关税，加拿大商品将于3月4日生效，同时对中国进口商品的额外关税，因为致命毒品仍在从这些国家涌入美国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 13:56:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-says-mexico-canada-tariffs-take-effect-march-4-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国小米价格豪华电轿车比最初促进的低35％</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-prices-luxury-electric-sedan-72932-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国的小米周四将其豪华电动轿车SU7 Ultra的初始标价降低了三分之一至529,900元（72,931.72美元），对世界上最大的汽车市场的特斯拉和波斯奇等人带来了更大的挑战。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 13:14:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-prices-luxury-electric-sedan-72932-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着贸易战的升级，经济学家押注中国的韧性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/trade-war-escalates-economists-bet-china-resilience-2025-02-27/</link><description>随着中国处于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税议程的最前沿，国内经济学家预计，随着贸易战的加剧，政策措施，供应链调整和加强全球合作伙伴关系的结合，加强了全球第二大经济体。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 12:19:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/trade-war-escalates-economists-bet-china-resilience-2025-02-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>